      <title>马尔代夫要求印度在三月中旬之前撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/maldives-tells-india-to-remove-its-troops-by-mid-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫总统告诉印度，必须在三月份之前从该岛撤军，兑现了他与中国走近时做出的选举承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/maldives-tells-india-to-remove-its-troops-by-mid-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国击落从也门胡塞地区发射的巡航导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/us-shoots-down-cruise-missile-fired-from-houthi-area-in-yemen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国军方表示，美国战斗机击落了一枚从也门胡塞武装地区向红海南部执行任务的海军驱逐舰发射的巡航导弹，并补充说没有人员伤亡或损坏的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/us-shoots-down-cruise-missile-fired-from-houthi-area-in-yemen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 02:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着军备关系的建立，朝鲜派遣外交部长访问俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/north-korea-sends-foreign-minister-to-russia-as-arms-ties-build</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜外交部长崔善姬启程前往俄罗斯，这可能会促成弗拉基米尔·普京总统访问平壤，并加强武器转让，以补充克里姆林宫攻击乌克兰的军火库。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/north-korea-sends-foreign-minister-to-russia-as-arms-ties-build</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 02:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国会公布临时支出法案以避免停工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/us-congress-unveils-temporary-spending-bill-to-avert-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国立法者于 1 月 20 日发布了一项权宜之计的支出法案，以避免政府部分关闭，这大大降低了关闭的可能性，但可能会激怒众议院议长迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 的保守派共和党人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/us-congress-unveils-temporary-spending-bill-to-avert-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 01:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国代表团抵达台湾会见蔡英文及其他官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/us-delegation-arrives-in-taiwan-to-meet-tsai-other-officials</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群前美国官员抵达台湾会见即将卸任的总统蔡英文，此次会谈将考验华盛顿和北京之间在台湾举行关键选举后近期关系的改善情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/us-delegation-arrives-in-taiwan-to-meet-tsai-other-officials</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 01:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔丹预测议长约翰逊将拒绝参议院边境协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/johnson-will-reject-bipartisan-senate-border-deal-jordan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院两党精心斡旋达成的边界妥协方案将在众议院一经达成就注定会失败——众议院司法委员会主席吉姆·乔丹表示，这将引起议长迈克·约翰逊的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/johnson-will-reject-bipartisan-senate-border-deal-jordan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:34:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从德克萨斯州到艾伯塔省，严寒考验着电网</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/bone-chilling-cold-is-testing-power-grids-from-texas-to-alberta</link>
      <description><![CDATA[席卷北美的北极风暴增加了停电的风险。由于预计天气仍将更加寒冷，从德克萨斯州到阿尔伯塔省的电网将继续面临压力，部分电价已经飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/bone-chilling-cold-is-testing-power-grids-from-texas-to-alberta</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 20:10:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举结果被视为迫使妥协，台湾股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/taiwan-election-result-to-force-compromise-in-boost-for-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政的民进党在总统选举中获胜，但失去了立法多数，台湾基准股指上涨，引发了中国的温和反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/taiwan-election-result-to-force-compromise-in-boost-for-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 16:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被定罪的俄罗斯前市长因同意在乌克兰作战而减少了监禁时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-14/convicted-former-russian-mayor-cuts-jail-time-short-by-agreeing-to-fight-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体周日报道，一名因受贿而被定罪的名誉扫地的俄罗斯前市长在签署与俄罗斯军队在乌克兰作战的合同后被缩短刑期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-14/convicted-former-russian-mayor-cuts-jail-time-short-by-agreeing-to-fight-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 12:42:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在台湾选举失利后，习近平几乎没有什么好的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/xi-s-taiwan-strategy-in-tatters-after-winnable-vote-slips-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在台湾选举中取得有利结果的希望破灭的那一刻并不是在本周末发生的，而是在11月的一个周四晚上在台北市中心的一家豪华酒店发生的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/xi-s-taiwan-strategy-in-tatters-after-winnable-vote-slips-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
